T1  - Unexpected Consequences of Improving Workplace Justice: A Six-Year Time Series Assessment
AU  - Mesch, Debra J.
AU  - Dalton, Dan R.
Y1  - 1992/12/01
PY  - 1992
DA  - 1992/12/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/256543
